Package com.technologica.registration.deferred

Class TechnologicaFluids

java.lang.Object
com.technologica.registration.deferred.util.MasterDeferredRegistrar
com.technologica.registration.deferred.TechnologicaFluids
public final class TechnologicaFluids extends MasterDeferredRegistrar

This class contains Registry Objects for Fluids. The init() method is called by Technologica.initDeferredRegisters() and returns a head-count to later be checked during registration and other setup activities.

Status:
GREEN
